data.description: This 4-bedroom 2.5 bath, 2 Car Garage is located in SE Raleigh. Walking distance to Coastal Credit Union Music Park. AC replaced October 2023, interior & trim freshly painted throughout the home, Roof updated 2022, toilets replaced in all bathrooms, downstairs bathroom sink replaced, front exterior lights replaced, master bath features a garden tub and walk in closet, new flooring in kitchen 2022, furnace replaced 2016. This home is located close to White Oak, Amazon & I40 with easy access to downtown.
